name: Qui-Gon Jinn
Lore: 'Accepted Obi-Wan Kenobi as his Padawan learner. Was given orders to protect Queen Amidala at all costs.',
Text: 'Deploys -2 to Tatooine. Power +1 at same site as Maul. Once during a duel Qui-Gon is in, may cancel a duel destiny just drawn and cause a redraw. Opponent''s aliens are power -1 at same site. Immune to attrition.',
